    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1905-10-20T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1905-10-20T00:00:00-05:00" n="913"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d913">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Emperor of Japan</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1905-10-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 20, 1905</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I thank Your Majesty for your kind expression of appreciation of the services I
                    was permitted to render in the cause of peace. It is to me very gratifying that
                    the treatment accorded to the Japanese plenipotentiaries in the United States
                    was such as to merit so cordial a recognition on the part of Your Majesty.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Theodore Roosevelt.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
